data.description: Welcome to this move-in-ready, charming Ranch style home featuring 3 spacious bedrooms w/ 2 full baths. Original wood floors, new carpet and fresh paint throughout, creates a warm and inviting atmosphere. Upgraded kitchen showcases a large center island, granite countertops, ceramic floors, ample cabinets & counter space. Dual garages plus an extra storage unit can be used as a workshop, man cave, etc. Rocking chair front porch & oversized deck is perfect for outdoor relaxation. Located in a desirable established community, just minutes away from I-85 Hwy & the up and coming downtown Mt. Holly - offering great restaurants, shopping & entertainment. This home is priced to sell & awaits its new owner! NO HOA!! FREE 1-year Home Warranty included!
